    "description": "《Soul of Roses》是一款 2D 流氓轻动作游戏。<br>吸收敌人的能力，战斗、死亡、复活，不断重复，以推进故事情节。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/3e9b45a6ea7ecc17cda1bfdfb46592f8.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/3e9b45a6ea7ecc17cda1bfdfb46592f8.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/3e9b45a6ea7ecc17cda1bfdfb46592f8.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >格里高利之家是什么？</h2>它是另一个时空的一家旅馆，在现实世界中没有得到满足的灵魂可以来到这里。<br>这个世界的居民都释放了自己的欲望，过着自己喜欢的生活。<br>在格里高利之家，&quot;思想的力量 &quot;就是一切。<br>即使肉体消亡，只要心灵不受伤害，就可以拒绝死亡。<br>其他居民也是如此。<br>这就是为什么把居民打成肉酱是安全的。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/16d5d1f9907d6c037d4a6911e21102d7.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=292 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >记忆之战</h2>格里高利之家遭到失控僵尸的袭击，陷入困境。<br>一觉醒来，你变成了僵尸中的一员，却连自己的名字都不记得了。<br>格里高利之家的看守人格里高利向你提供了一份合约。<br>如果你能恢复格里高利之家的和平，我就帮你恢复记忆。<br>你为恢复格里高利之家的和平和你自己的记忆而展开的战斗开始了。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/8aecc8f4ecab3df1efabf3ba675f3707.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/8aecc8f4ecab3df1efabf3ba675f3707.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/8aecc8f4ecab3df1efabf3ba675f3707.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与灵魂捕手一起转变！</h2>用灵魂摄取器摄取敌人的灵魂，这是一个镶嵌在你手中的神秘装置。<br>吃掉你摄取的灵魂，你就能变身为反映对手能力的灵魂样式！<br>敌人有多少，灵魂就有多少，所以你一定能找到最适合自己的灵魂风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/671cad35b7f32b26c2fd0750d260ec39.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/671cad35b7f32b26c2fd0750d260ec39.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/671cad35b7f32b26c2fd0750d260ec39.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的战斗方式！</h2>结合 “记忆 ”和 “灵魂风格 ”来强化自己，找到属于自己的战斗方式！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/678cd7afd780c2aad92164c52fb0b49f.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/678cd7afd780c2aad92164c52fb0b49f.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/678cd7afd780c2aad92164c52fb0b49f.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >好友合作！</h2>在双人合作模式中与朋友一起游戏！<br>在本地合作模式或使用 Steam 的 “远程同屏游戏 ”功能进行联机，一起与敌人作战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/00213bab53cb2d46637ca511e799d340.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/00213bab53cb2d46637ca511e799d340.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/00213bab53cb2d46637ca511e799d340.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有趣的居民</h2>这里有许多色彩缤纷、可爱又略带滑稽的居民！<br>你可以和他们尽情聊天，也可以把他们的灵魂掏出来吃掉。",
